%% Part 2 — Live Data Lane (Aggregator Pattern)
%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'linear', 'nodeSpacing': 65, 'rankSpacing': 80}}}%%
flowchart TD
    User([👤 Customer])
    Bot[🤖 SadaDost Bot]

    subgraph Auth["🔐 Auth Service"]
        direction TB
        AuthSvc[Generates UUID<br/>Issues signed JWT]
        UsersDB[(users DB)]
        AuthSvc --> UsersDB
    end

    subgraph GW["🚪 API Gateway / Aggregator"]
        direction TB
        Decode[Decode JWT<br/>extract user_id UUID]
        Fan[Parallel fan-out<br/>asyncio.gather + timeout]
        Stitch[Stitch → one JSON<br/>tiered failure handling]
        Decode --> Fan --> Stitch
    end

    subgraph Services["🏦 Owning Microservices — each strips restricted fields"]
        direction TB
        KYC["KYC API :8081<br/>(critical)"]
        Bal["Balance API :8082<br/>(critical)"]
        Card["Cards API :8083<br/>(non-critical)"]
        Txn["Transactions API :8084<br/>(non-critical)"]
    end

    User -->|login| Bot
    AuthSvc -.->|signed JWT| Bot
    Bot -->|"1 request — GET /user-profile<br/>Authorization: JWT"| Decode

    Fan -->|GET /kyc/uuid| KYC
    Fan -->|GET /balance/uuid| Bal
    Fan -->|GET /cards/uuid| Card
    Fan -->|GET /transactions/uuid| Txn

    KYC -. allowed fields only .-> Stitch
    Bal -. allowed fields only .-> Stitch
    Card -. "[] on timeout" .-> Stitch
    Txn -. "[] on timeout" .-> Stitch

    Stitch -->|single aggregated payload| Bot
    Bot -->|answer| User
